{"tid":617432,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣好想睇到高鐵同條大橋收皮？","createTime":"2018-04-05T03:11:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T04:49:45.000Z","uid":167329,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"07c91038ac89cdc9b0bf7dffdbb37c5b17332a57","tid":617432,"uid":167329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T03:11:25.000Z","msg":"我唔知我咁諗啱唔啱啦 <br />\n<br />\n先不討論高鐵同條橋係咪真係有用先。<br />\n<br />\n政府之前擺兩條法案係到死都唔換 迫住市民接受 <br />\n啲人話高鐵唔好整地下 終點唔好係西九 唔聽<br />\n條橋唔洗係海底 整高啲比船過到就得 唔聽<br />\n家陣有事啦 日日都等住聽到佢地收皮既新聞.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b623585e7a2679163430225993bc0346eaacfaf","tid":617432,"uid":132296,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T03:12:31.000Z","msg":"屌，收咗皮咪又係搵我地埋單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地無得揀"},{"pid":"e315b101d9b0be26b4015155e28c5831a8d4a881","tid":617432,"uid":91664,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4b623585e7a2679163430225993bc0346eaacfaf","tid":617432,"uid":132296,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T03:12:31.000Z","msg":"屌，收咗皮咪又係搵我地埋單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地無得揀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T03:15:30.000Z","msg":"係唔係我哋埋單，啲錢都唔會過我哋手啦"},{"pid":"559faf58aeeef4ff075288647ab811017bea1bcb","tid":617432,"uid":167329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4b623585e7a2679163430225993bc0346eaacfaf","tid":617432,"uid":132296,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T03:12:31.000Z","msg":"屌，收咗皮咪又係搵我地埋單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地無得揀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T04:49:45.000Z","msg":"其實政府稅收有一半都係賣地 所以算一半我地錢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我都唔知咁諗啱唔啱"}]}